tly\nhigh metallicity for its SMBH mass and luminosity. Our earlier work suggests\nthat host galaxy mass, correlated with SMBH mass and AGN luminosity, is the\nfundamental parameter affecting BLR metallicities. Some secondary effect, not\nrelated to L/Ledd, must be enhancing the metallicities in NLS1s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2004 21:38:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
